{"text_id":10051,"tokens":["The"," min","-","sum"," decoding"," algorithm"," is"," widely"," used"," for"," forward"," error"," correction"," (","FEC",")"," in"," various"," coding"," schemes",","," such"," as"," the"," low","-","density"," parity","-","check"," (","LD","PC",")"," and"," the"," convolutional"," code","."," Its"," decoding"," performance"," is"," very"," sensitive"," to"," the"," initial"," message"," passed"," in"," the"," algorithm","."," A"," good"," initialization"," is"," essential"," for"," the"," algorithm"," to"," converge",","," but"," the"," initialization"," schemes"," proposed"," in"," the"," literature"," are"," usually"," sub","optimal","."," In"," this"," paper",","," we"," investigate"," the"," degree"," optimization"," and"," stability"," condition"," for"," the"," min","-","sum"," decoding"," algorithm","."," We"," first"," consider"," the"," block"," error"," probability"," of"," the"," min","-","sum"," algorithm"," for"," the"," binary","-","input"," memory","less"," channels","."," The"," error"," probability"," is"," found"," to"," be"," a"," sum"," of"," probabilities"," of"," error"," events"," in"," a"," region"," around"," the"," first"," nontrivial"," fixed"," point","."," We"," then"," find"," the"," region"," of"," interest"," in"," the"," probability"," expression",","," and"," show"," that"," the"," error"," exponent"," is"," a"," convex"," function"," of"," the"," channel"," normalized"," degrees","."," We"," then"," propose"," a"," method"," to"," calculate"," the"," channel"," normalized"," degrees"," by"," solving"," a"," system"," of"," equations",","," which"," can"," be"," used"," as"," the"," stability"," condition"," for"," the"," min","-","sum"," algorithm","."," Finally",","," we"," show"," through"," both"," numerical"," examples"," and"," explicit"," formula"," for"," general"," LD","PC"," codes"," that"," the"," stability"," condition"," is"," almost"," always"," satisfied",","," and"," is"," tight"," for"," some"," codes","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"dolly","label":1}